      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "WEBLEC MEMPHIS (1) jumped favourite and was too quick with an all-the-way win last start (34.52) at this track in a Restricted WIN H over 595m. Has a strong record out of this box with two wins and two minor placings from four starts. Makes plenty of appeal on the back of that last-start win. MEPUNGA SHADOW (2) made light work of the tricky draw with a fast early sectional but gathered in and had to settle for the minors, finishing second (34.84) at this track over 595m. Ran one of the fastest times on the program last start despite finishing in the minors. Leading chance. LAMIA TAYA (4) finished fourth last time but the start prior broke the clock when winning over 600m at The Meadows, taking a Grade 4/5 in a quick 34.43. Smart winner two back and looks a key chance on that form. OUTSIDES (6) is always hard to beat when drawn in this box.",
